node.title: Whopper of a crash: Driver flees after flipping car onto its side in Auckland Burger King drive-thru
node.description: Newshub captured the aftermath of the crash.
node.content: ["A driver who crashed their car into an Auckland Burger King drive-thru fled the scene in another vehicle, police say.", "Newshub captured the aftermath of the crash which left a white sedan flipped onto its side outside the Sylvia Park Burger King.", "Police said they received a report of a crash between a car and a building on Mt Wellington Highway at about 12:25am on Thursday.\n", "\"The driver of that vehicle then got into another vehicle and left the scene.\"", "Police said no one was injured and and enquiries into the crash are ongoing."]
